I understand product development, quality, and functionality likely contribute to capital raise valuations, and timing is critical.

I'm just listening to many expert podcasts and the speed of AI development is mind-blowing. I very much understand that ATMTA is leveraging AI to the highest degree, but just curious on your general thoughts.

